              teachingCode: 'from Bio.Seq import Seq\n\n# Create a DNA sequence\nseq = Seq("ATGCGATCGA")\n\n# Complement (same direction)\nseq.complement()       # Seq("TACGCTAGCT")\n\n# Reverse complement (5\'→3\' of opposite strand)\nseq.reverse_complement()  # Seq("TCGATCGCAT")\n\n# Transcribe DNA to RNA\nseq.transcribe()       # Seq("AUGCGAUCGA")\n\n# Seq objects also support slicing\nseq[0:3]  # Seq("ATG") — the start codon',
