              teachingCode: 'from tensorflow.keras import layers\n\n# Dense layer with 64 neurons and ReLU activation\nlayers.Dense(64, activation="relu")\n\n# Output layer for binary classification\nlayers.Dense(1, activation="sigmoid")\n\n# Output layer for multi-class (e.g., 5 cancer subtypes)\nlayers.Dense(5, activation="softmax")\n\n# Regression output (no activation = linear)\nlayers.Dense(1)  # predicts continuous value',
              question: 'Complete the code to create a Dense hidden layer with 128 neurons and ReLU activation:',
