              correctAnswer: 'The model is overfitting — memorizing training data but losing generalization',
              explanation: 'When training loss decreases but validation loss increases, the model is overfitting: it memorizes training patterns that do not generalize. Solutions include Dropout, EarlyStopping, and more training data.',
