              options: ['["weight"]', '.weight', '("weight")', '.get_weight()'],
              correctAnswer: '["weight"]',
              explanation: 'Edge attributes are accessed via dictionary-style indexing: G.edges[u,v]["weight"]. Node attributes use the same pattern: G.nodes[n]["attribute"].',
