              teachingCode: 'import networkx as nx\n\n# Read edge list (simple format)\nG = nx.read_edgelist("ppi_network.txt")\n\n# With edge attributes\nG = nx.read_edgelist("ppi_weighted.txt", data=True)\n\n# Specify data types\nG = nx.read_edgelist("network.txt",\n    nodetype=int, data=(("weight", float),))\n\n# Write edge list\nnx.write_edgelist(G, "output.txt")\n\n# Also supports: GML, GraphML, GEXF formats\nG = nx.read_gml("network.gml")',
